Enum Class SceneOptions

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<SceneOptions>
project.chenlin_17.tools.SceneOptions
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<SceneOptions>, Constable
public enum SceneOptions extends Enum<SceneOptions>
Each constructor has its set value for brickSets,background music,background image and ball image.
The enum name stands for the specific theme choice.
